title: OpenVINO model server example fails...
body:
Hiii , 

I am currently working on this in ubuntu 18.04  machine [https://github.com/openvinotoolkit/model_server/blob/main/docs/face_detection_script_example.md](url) 

My models were placed at models/model1/1/facedetection.xml

I can able to start the docker using this command : - 

**docker run -d -v $(pwd)/model:/models -p 9000:9000 openvino/model_server:latest  --model_path /models/model1/1 --model_name face-detection --port 9000  --shape auto**
I don't know whether this command is correct or not .. If any changes need to made in previous command. Let me know

But when Iam running the **face_detection.py** file
It shows the error like this 

2020-12-28 13:17:59.263573: W tensorflow/stream_executor/platform/default/dso_loader.cc:60] Could not load dynamic library 'libcudart.so.11.0'; dlerror: libcudart.so.11.0: cannot open shared object file: No such file or directory

['people1.jpeg', 'people2.jpeg', 'people3.jpeg', 'people4.jpeg']

    result = stub.Predict(request, 10.0) # result includes a dictionary with all model outputs

  File "/my_tensorflow/venv/lib/python3.6/site-packages/grpc/_channel.py", line 729, in _end_unary_response_blocking

	details = "failed to connect to all addresses"
	debug_error_string = "{"created":"@1609141680.374217669","description":"Failed to pick subchannel","file":"src/core/ext/filters/client_channel/client_channel.cc","file_line":4133,"referenced_errors":[{"created":"@1609141680.374209599","description":"failed to connect to all addresses","file":"src/core/ext/filters/client_channel/lb_policy/pick_first/pick_first.cc","file_line":397,"grpc_status":14}]}"


please help me to work on this issue
Thanks in advance...
